## 1. Executive Summary & Tech Stack

The DPAH Frontend is a React 19 single-page application serving as the internal AI control plane for Data Patterns employees. It provides role-based access to domain-specific AI agent chat interfaces (RMS, MRR, SCM, HRMS, Finance, IT, OPS), timesheet management, and chat history navigation.

