| **Routing** | React Router DOM 7.5.2 | Client-side routing with lazy loading |
| **State Management** | Zustand 5.0.10 | Global state (available but not currently used for core flows) |
| **HTTP Client** | Axios 1.9.0 + native `fetch` | API calls (api.js uses native fetch; axios is a listed dependency) |
