## 7. Color Palette & Theme System

### Dual Theme Approach

The app uses **two complementary theme strategies**:

1. **`body.light-mode` class toggle** — Applied to `<body>` element. All custom `@layer components` CSS classes in [index.css](src/index.css) have `.light-mode` override selectors. Theme state persisted in `localStorage.lightMode`.
2. **`dark:` Tailwind prefix** — Used directly in JSX alongside custom classes for components that rely purely on Tailwind utilities (e.g., FormRenderer).

