| **Chat overlay width** | `@media (min-width: 1024px) { width: calc(100% - 280px) }` | Full-screen on mobile, sidebar-respecting on desktop |
| **Chat overlay collapsed** | `@media (min-width: 1024px) { body.sidebar-collapsed .chat-overlay { width: calc(100% - 88px) } }` | Accounts for collapsed sidebar |
| **Sidebar** | `w-[280px]` expanded, `body.sidebar-collapsed .sidebar { width: 88px }` | Class-based collapse, no media query |
| **Main content** | `ml-[280px]` expanded, `body.sidebar-collapsed .main-content { ml-[88px] }` | Follows sidebar |
| **Settings grid** | `grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8` | Single → triple column |
| **Settings profile stats** | `grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4` | Single → double column |
| **Form fields** | `grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-5` | Single → double column |
| **Textareas** | `md:col-span-2` | Full-width on medium+ |
| **Chat padding** | `px-4 md:px-12 pb-40` | Tight on mobile, spacious on desktop |
| **Input area** | `px-4 md:px-12` | Responsive horizontal padding |
| **Timesheet tables** | `overflow-x-auto` | Horizontal scroll on small screens |
| **Chat tables** | `overflow-x-auto max-h-[400px]` | Scrollable with height cap |
| **Hero title** | `text-3xl` → inherited | No responsive size change |
| **Section title** | `text-[13px]` | Fixed small size |

### No Media Queries for Sidebar

The sidebar uses **class-based width toggling** (no media queries):
- Expanded: `w-[280px]`, sidebar-nav visible, logo visible, system-status text visible
- Collapsed: `body.sidebar-collapsed` class → `w-[88px]`, text hidden, icons centered, status becomes circle-only

